review_460504490~“A night away”~Never knew this great hotel was in Brisbane. Very close to all amenities and vaule for money.  Staff were friendly and professional.  I had forgotten my phone charger and they had several types for hire as well as shaving kits etc. Very thoughtful.  I would definately come back  ~4~5~5~4~4~4~4~nan
